        var UGERROR = {
            errors: [],
            loggerLoaded: false,
        };
        var oldOnError = window.onerror;
        var loadScript = function(src, resolve) {
            UGERROR.loggerLoaded = true;
            var script = document.createElement('script');
            script.async=true;
            script.type = 'text/javascript';
            script.src = src;

            var changeState = function() {
                if (!loaded) {
                    resolve()
                    loaded = true;
                }
            };
            var loaded;

            script.onreadystatechange = changeState;
            script.onload = changeState;

            var node = document.getElementsByTagName('script')[0];
            node.parentNode.insertBefore(script, node);
        };

        UGERROR.loadErrorLogger = function (release) {
            var whitelistUrls = [
                new RegExp('https://www.ultimate-guitar.com/static/public')
            ];

            if (window.location.pathname !== '/') {
                whitelistUrls.push(new RegExp(window.location.href))
            }

            var tags = {
                source: 'ug',
                country: 'AU',
                isProUser: false,
                isAuthenticated: true,
                userId: '25758087',
            };

            !UGERROR.loggerLoaded && loadScript('//www.ultimate-guitar.com/static/vendor/centry/raven.min.js', function() {
                window.onerror = oldOnError;
                window.Raven.setUserContext({
                    userId: '25758087'
                });
                window.Raven.config('https://c21f4a3b0a5844b890e73c7216e537ac@sentry.ultimate-guitar.com/4', {
                    release: release,
                    whitelistUrls: whitelistUrls,
                    tags: tags
                }).install();
                UGERROR.errors.forEach(function(args) {
                    (args.length > 1) ? window.onerror.apply(this, args) : window.Raven.captureException(args);
                });
            })
        };

        window.onerror = function() {
            UGERROR.errors.push(arguments);
            oldOnError && oldOnError.apply(this, arguments);
        };

        window.addEventListener('load', function() {
            UGERROR.loadErrorLogger("_ver1551088175");
        })
    </script>

    (function(window) {
       window.__cmp = (function() {
            window.addEventListener('message', function(event) {
                window.__cmp.receiveMessage(event);
            });

            var commandQueue = [];
            var cmp = function(command, parameter, callback) {
                commandQueue.push({
                    command: command,
                    parameter: parameter,
                    callback: callback
                });
            };
            cmp.commandQueue = commandQueue;
            cmp.receiveMessage = function(event) {
                var data = event && event.data && event.data.__cmpCall;
                if (data) {
                    commandQueue.push({
                        callId: data.callId,
                        command: data.command,
                        parameter: data.parameter,
                        event: event
                    });
                }
            };
            cmp.config = {
                customPurposeListLocation: 'docs/purposes.json',
                globalConsentLocation: 'docs/portal.html',
                forceLocale: null,
                domain: '.ultimate-guitar.com'
            };
            return cmp;
        }());
    })(window);
</script>

            getAdomikRandomAdGroup: function () {
                var rand = Math.random()
                switch (true) {
                    case rand < 0.09:
                        return 'ad_ex' + (Math.floor(100 * (rand)))
                    case rand < 0.10:
                        return 'ad_bc'
                    default:
                        return 'ad_opt'
                }

                var path = '/' + dfpId + '/' + dfpCode;

            errors: [],
            loggerLoaded: false,
        };
        var oldOnError = window.onerror;
        var loadScript = function(src, resolve) {
            UGERROR.loggerLoaded = true;
            var script = document.createElement('script');
            script.async=true;
            script.type = 'text/javascript';
            script.src = src;

            var changeState = function() {
                if (!loaded) {
                    resolve()
                    loaded = true;
                }
            };
            var loaded;

            script.onreadystatechange = changeState;
            script.onload = changeState;

            var node = document.getElementsByTagName('script')[0];
            node.parentNode.insertBefore(script, node);
        };

        UGERROR.loadErrorLogger = function (release) {
            var whitelistUrls = [
                new RegExp('https://www.ultimate-guitar.com/static/public')
            ];

                whitelistUrls.push(new RegExp(window.location.href))
            }

                country: 'AU',

                userId: '25758087',
            };

                    userId: '25758087'
                });

                }).install();
                UGERROR.errors.forEach(function(args) {
                    (args.length > 1) ? window.onerror.apply(this, args) : window.Raven.captureException(args);
                });
            })
        };

        window.onerror = function() {
            UGERROR.errors.push(arguments);
            oldOnError && oldOnError.apply(this, arguments);
        };

        window.addEventListener('load', function() {
            UGERROR.loadErrorLogger("_ver1551088175");
        })

    <script>
    (function(window) {
       window.__cmp = (function() {
            window.addEventListener('message', function(event) {
                window.__cmp.receiveMessage(event);
            });

            var commandQueue = [];
            var cmp = function(command, parameter, callback) {
                commandQueue.push({
                    command: command,
                    parameter: parameter,
                    callback: callback
                });
            };
            cmp.commandQueue = commandQueue;
            cmp.receiveMessage = function(event) {
                var data = event && event.data && event.data.__cmpCall;
                if (data) {
                    commandQueue.push({
                        callId: data.callId,
                        command: data.command,
                        parameter: data.parameter,
                        event: event
                    });
                }
            };
            cmp.config = {
                customPurposeListLocation: 'docs/purposes.json',
                globalConsentLocation: 'docs/portal.html',
                forceLocale: null,
                domain: '.ultimate-guitar.com'
            };
            return cmp;
        }());
    })(window);
</script>

            apstagFetchBids: function (units, refresh) {
                if (!units || units.length === 0) {
                    return;
                }
                apstag.fetchBids({
                    slots: units.map(function (unit) {
                        return {
                            slotID: unit.code,
                            slotName: '/' + window.UGAPP.bidding.dfpId + '/' + unit.dfpCode + (refresh ? '_REFRESH' : ''),

            getAdomikRandomAdGroup: function () {
                var rand = Math.random()
                switch (true) {
                    case rand < 0.09:
                        return 'ad_ex' + (Math.floor(100 * (rand)))
                    case rand < 0.10:
                        return 'ad_bc'
                    default:
                        return 'ad_opt'
                }
            },
            defineGptTag: function (params, needRefresh) {
                var dfpId = window.UGAPP.bidding.dfpId
                var dfpCode = needRefresh ? params.dfpCode + '_REFRESH' : params.dfpCode;
                var path = '/' + dfpId + '/' + dfpCode;
                var tag = googletag
                    .defineSlot(path, params.sizes, params.code)
                    .addService(googletag.pubads())
                    .setTargeting('ad_group', biddingHelpers.getAdomikRandomAdGroup())
                    .setTargeting('is_refresh', '0');

                tag.setTargeting('allow_adx', window.UGAPP.bidding.disableAdx ? 'false' : 'true');
                tag.setTargeting('page_type', window.UGAPP.bidding.analytics.pageType);

                if (params.additionalSekindoBehavior) {
                    tag.setTargeting('video', 'sekindo');
                }




                return tag;
            },
            getUnitByCode: function (code) {
                return window.UGAPP.bidding.units.filter(function (unit) {
                    return unit.code === code
                })[0]
            },
            getSlotByCode: function (code) {
                var slots = window.UGAPP.bidding.slots.filter(function (slot) {
                    return slot.code === code

                return slots ? slots[0] : null
            }
        };

        window.googletag.cmd.push(function() {
            window.googletag.pubads().addEventListener('slotRenderEnded', function(e) {
                var slot = biddingHelpers.getSlotByCode(e.slot.getSlotElementId())
                if (!slot) {
                    return
                }

                if (
                    (
                        slot.code === 'ad_cs_2010319_300_250' // tab_desktop tab_pro_desktop для Secindo
                        && [138209404243, 138238546272, 138238996438, 138245687657, 138245691213, 138245902399, 138245692437, 138248215773, 138248239163].indexOf(e.sourceAgnosticCreativeId) !== -1
                    )
                    || (
                        slot.code === 'ad_cs_2010320_160_600' // tab_desktop
                        && [4954799754].indexOf(e.sourceAgnosticLineItemId) !== -1
                    )
                    || (
                        slot.code === 'ad_cs_5723252_300_250' // tab_mobile
                        && [4954799490].indexOf(e.sourceAgnosticLineItemId) !== -1
                    )
                ) {
                    slot.refresh = typeof slot.refresh === 'object' ? slot.refresh : {}
                    slot.refresh.enabled = false
                }
            })
        });


            </script>

            var UGERROR = {
                errors: [],
                loggerLoaded: false,
            };
            var oldOnError = window.onerror;
            var loadScript = function(src, resolve) {
                UGERROR.loggerLoaded = true;
                var script = document.createElement('script');
                script.async=true;
                script.type = 'text/javascript';
                script.src = src;

                var changeState = function() {
                    if (!loaded) {
                        resolve()
                        loaded = true;
                    }
                };
                var loaded;

                script.onreadystatechange = changeState;
                script.onload = changeState;

                var node = document.getElementsByTagName('script')[0];
                node.parentNode.insertBefore(script, node);
            };

            UGERROR.loadErrorLogger = function (release) {
                var whitelistUrls = [
                    new RegExp('https://www.ultimate-guitar.com/static/public')
                ];

                if (window.location.pathname !== '/') {
                    whitelistUrls.push(new RegExp(window.location.href))
                }

                var tags = {
                    source: 'ug',
                    country: 'AU',
                    isProUser: false,
                    isAuthenticated: true,
                    userId: '25758087',
                };

                !UGERROR.loggerLoaded && loadScript('//www.ultimate-guitar.com/static/vendor/centry/raven.min.js', function() {
                    window.onerror = oldOnError;
                    window.Raven.setUserContext({
                        userId: '25758087'
                    });
                    window.Raven.config('https://c21f4a3b0a5844b890e73c7216e537ac@sentry.ultimate-guitar.com/4', {
                        release: release,
                        whitelistUrls: whitelistUrls,
                        tags: tags
                    }).install();
                    UGERROR.errors.forEach(function(args) {
                        (args.length > 1) ? window.onerror.apply(this, args) : window.Raven.captureException(args);
                    });
                })
            };

            window.onerror = function() {
                UGERROR.errors.push(arguments);

        <script>
        (function(window) {
           window.__cmp = (function() {
                window.addEventListener('message', function(event) {
                    window.__cmp.receiveMessage(event);
                });

                var commandQueue = [];
                var cmp = function(command, parameter, callback) {
                    commandQueue.push({
                        command: command,
                        parameter: parameter,
                        callback: callback
                    });
                };
                cmp.commandQueue = commandQueue;
                cmp.receiveMessage = function(event) {
                    var data = event && event.data && event.data.__cmpCall;
                    if (data) {
                        commandQueue.push({
                            callId: data.callId,
                            command: data.command,
                            parameter: data.parameter,
                            event: event
                        });
                    }
                };
                cmp.config = {
                    customPurposeListLocation: 'docs/purposes.json',
                    globalConsentLocation: 'docs/portal.html',
                    forceLocale: null,
                    domain: '.ultimate-guitar.com'
                };
                return cmp;
            }());
        })(window);
    </script>

                    var rand = Math.random()
                    switch (true) {
                        case rand < 0.09:
                            return 'ad_ex' + (Math.floor(100 * (rand)))

                            return 'ad_bc'

    <script>
    (function(window) {
       window.__cmp = (function() {
            window.addEventListener('message', function(event) {
                window.__cmp.receiveMessage(event);
            });

            var commandQueue = [];
            var cmp = function(command, parameter, callback) {
                commandQueue.push({
                    command: command,
                    parameter: parameter,
                    callback: callback
                });
            };
            cmp.commandQueue = commandQueue;
            cmp.receiveMessage = function(event) {
                var data = event && event.data && event.data.__cmpCall;
                if (data) {
                    commandQueue.push({
                        callId: data.callId,
                        command: data.command,
                        parameter: data.parameter,
                        event: event
                    });
                }
            };
            cmp.config = {
                customPurposeListLocation: 'docs/purposes.json',
                globalConsentLocation: 'docs/portal.html',
                forceLocale: null,
                domain: '.ultimate-guitar.com'
            };
            return cmp;
        }());
    })(window);
</script>

        var UGERROR = {
            errors: [],
            loggerLoaded: false,
        };
        var oldOnError = window.onerror;
        var loadScript = function(src, resolve) {
            UGERROR.loggerLoaded = true;
            var script = document.createElement('script');
            script.async=true;
            script.type = 'text/javascript';
            script.src = src;

            var changeState = function() {
                if (!loaded) {
                    resolve()
                    loaded = true;
                }
            };
            var loaded;

            script.onreadystatechange = changeState;
            script.onload = changeState;

            var node = document.getElementsByTagName('script')[0];
            node.parentNode.insertBefore(script, node);
        };

        UGERROR.loadErrorLogger = function (release) {
            var whitelistUrls = [
                new RegExp('https://www.ultimate-guitar.com/static/public')
            ];

            if (window.location.pathname !== '/') {
                whitelistUrls.push(new RegExp(window.location.href))
            }

            var tags = {
                source: 'ug',
                country: 'AU',
                isProUser: false,
                isAuthenticated: true,
                userId: '25758087',
            };

            !UGERROR.loggerLoaded && loadScript('//www.ultimate-guitar.com/static/vendor/centry/raven.min.js', function() {
                window.onerror = oldOnError;
                window.Raven.setUserContext({
                    userId: '25758087'
                });
                window.Raven.config('https://c21f4a3b0a5844b890e73c7216e537ac@sentry.ultimate-guitar.com/4', {
                    release: release,
                    whitelistUrls: whitelistUrls,
                    tags: tags
                }).install();
                UGERROR.errors.forEach(function(args) {
                    (args.length > 1) ? window.onerror.apply(this, args) : window.Raven.captureException(args);
                });
            })
        };

        window.onerror = function() {
            UGERROR.errors.push(arguments);
            oldOnError && oldOnError.apply(this, arguments);
        };

        window.addEventListener('load', function() {
            UGERROR.loadErrorLogger("_ver1551088175");
        })
    </script>

    <script>
    (function(window) {
       window.__cmp = (function() {
            window.addEventListener('message', function(event) {
                window.__cmp.receiveMessage(event);
            });

            var commandQueue = [];
            var cmp = function(command, parameter, callback) {
                commandQueue.push({
                    command: command,
                    parameter: parameter,
                    callback: callback
                });
            };
            cmp.commandQueue = commandQueue;
            cmp.receiveMessage = function(event) {
                var data = event && event.data && event.data.__cmpCall;
                if (data) {
                    commandQueue.push({
                        callId: data.callId,
                        command: data.command,
                        parameter: data.parameter,
                        event: event
                    });
                }
            };
            cmp.config = {
                customPurposeListLocation: 'docs/purposes.json',
                globalConsentLocation: 'docs/portal.html',
                forceLocale: null,
                domain: '.ultimate-guitar.com'
            };
            return cmp;
        }());
    })(window);
</script>

                var rand = Math.random()
                switch (true) {
                    case rand < 0.09:
                        return 'ad_ex' + (Math.floor(100 * (rand)))

                        return 'ad_bc'

        var UGERROR = {
            errors: [],
            loggerLoaded: false,
        };
        var oldOnError = window.onerror;
        var loadScript = function(src, resolve) {
            UGERROR.loggerLoaded = true;
            var script = document.createElement('script');
            script.async=true;
            script.type = 'text/javascript';
            script.src = src;

            var changeState = function() {
                if (!loaded) {
                    resolve()
                    loaded = true;
                }
            };
            var loaded;

            script.onreadystatechange = changeState;
            script.onload = changeState;

            var node = document.getElementsByTagName('script')[0];
            node.parentNode.insertBefore(script, node);
        };

        UGERROR.loadErrorLogger = function (release) {
            var whitelistUrls = [
                new RegExp('https://www.ultimate-guitar.com/static/public')
            ];

            if (window.location.pathname !== '/') {
                whitelistUrls.push(new RegExp(window.location.href))
            }

            var tags = {
                source: 'ug',
                country: 'AU',
                isProUser: false,
                isAuthenticated: true,
                userId: '25758087',
            };

            !UGERROR.loggerLoaded && loadScript('//www.ultimate-guitar.com/static/vendor/centry/raven.min.js', function() {
                window.onerror = oldOnError;
                window.Raven.setUserContext({
                    userId: '25758087'
                });
                window.Raven.config('https://c21f4a3b0a5844b890e73c7216e537ac@sentry.ultimate-guitar.com/4', {
                    release: release,
                    whitelistUrls: whitelistUrls,
                    tags: tags
                }).install();
                UGERROR.errors.forEach(function(args) {
                    (args.length > 1) ? window.onerror.apply(this, args) : window.Raven.captureException(args);
                });
            })
        };

        window.onerror = function() {
            UGERROR.errors.push(arguments);
            oldOnError && oldOnError.apply(this, arguments);
        };

        window.addEventListener('load', function() {
            UGERROR.loadErrorLogger("_ver1551088175");
        })

    <script>
    (function(window) {
       window.__cmp = (function() {
            window.addEventListener('message', function(event) {
                window.__cmp.receiveMessage(event);
            });

            var commandQueue = [];
            var cmp = function(command, parameter, callback) {
                commandQueue.push({
                    command: command,
                    parameter: parameter,
                    callback: callback
                });
            };
            cmp.commandQueue = commandQueue;
            cmp.receiveMessage = function(event) {
                var data = event && event.data && event.data.__cmpCall;
                if (data) {
                    commandQueue.push({
                        callId: data.callId,
                        command: data.command,
                        parameter: data.parameter,
                        event: event
                    });
                }
            };
            cmp.config = {
                customPurposeListLocation: 'docs/purposes.json',
                globalConsentLocation: 'docs/portal.html',
                forceLocale: null,
                domain: '.ultimate-guitar.com'
            };
            return cmp;
        }());
    })(window);
</script>

        window.UGAPP.bidding.slots = window.UGAPP.bidding.units.map(function (unit) {
            return {
                code: unit.code,
                appnexusPlacementId: unit.appnexusPlacementId,
                refresh: unit.refresh || {},
                tag: null,
                dynamic: unit.dynamic,
                needDecreaseRefreshDelayMetrics: unit.needDecreaseRefreshDelayMetrics,
                decreaseRefreshDelayMetricsCoefficient: unit.decreaseRefreshDelayMetricsCoefficient,
            }
        })

                var pbjs = pbjs || {};
        pbjs.que = pbjs.que || [];

                var googletag = window.googletag || {};
        googletag.cmd = googletag.cmd || [];

                var biddingHelpers = {
            gptLoaded: false,
            loadScript: function (src, errCb) {
                var script = document.createElement('script');
                script.async = true;
                script.type = 'text/javascript';
                script.src = src;
                if (typeof errCb === 'function') {
                    script.addEventListener('error', errCb);
                }
                var node = document.getElementsByTagName('script')[0];
                node.parentNode.insertBefore(script, node);
            },
            loadPrebid: function () {
                this.loadScript('https://www.ultimate-guitar.com/static/public/build/prebid/prebid_ver1551088175.js', function() {
                    window.UGAPP.bidding.prebidLoadError = true;
                });
            },
            loadAmazonApstag: function () {
                !function (a9, a, p, s, t, A, g) {
                    if (a[a9]) return;

                    function q(c, r) {
                        a[a9]._Q.push([c, r])
                    }

                    a[a9] = {
                        init: function () {
                            q("i", arguments)
                        },
                        fetchBids: function () {
                            q("f", arguments)
                        },
                        setDisplayBids: function () {
                        },
                        targetingKeys: function () {
                            return []
                        }, _Q: []
                    };
                    A = p.createElement(s);
                    A.async = !0;
                    A.src = t;
                    g = p.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];
                    g.parentNode.insertBefore(A, g)
                }("apstag", window, document, "script", "//c.amazon-adsystem.com/aax2/apstag.js");

                var apstagParams = {
                    pubID: 'fa84ab71-a984-4d4b-9cab-fa3b3879ff93',
                    adServer: 'googletag',
                }

                if (window.UGAPP.bidding.isGDPRAvailable) {
                    apstagParams.gdpr = {
                        enabled: true,
                        cmpTimeout: 100000000
                    }
                }

                apstag.init(apstagParams)
            },
            apstagFetchBids: function (units, refresh) {
                if (!units || units.length === 0) {
                    return;
                }
                apstag.fetchBids({
                    slots: units.map(function (unit) {
                        return {
                            slotID: unit.code,
                            slotName: '/' + window.UGAPP.bidding.dfpId + '/' + unit.dfpCode + (refresh ? '_REFRESH' : ''),
                            sizes: unit.sizes
                        };
                    }),
                    timeout: window.UGAPP.bidding.timeout
                }, function (bids) {
                    googletag.cmd.push(function () {
                        apstag.setDisplayBids()
                    })
                })
            },
            loadAdServer: function () {
                if (this.gptLoaded) return;
                this.loadScript('//www.googletagservices.com/tag/js/gpt.js');
                this.gptLoaded = true;
            },
            getAdomikRandomAdGroup: function () {
                var rand = Math.random()
                switch (true) {
                    case rand < 0.09:
                        return 'ad_ex' + (Math.floor(100 * (rand)))
                    case rand < 0.10:
                        return 'ad_bc'
                    default:
                        return 'ad_opt'
                }
            },
            defineGptTag: function (params, needRefresh) {
                var dfpId = window.UGAPP.bidding.dfpId
                var dfpCode = needRefresh ? params.dfpCode + '_REFRESH' : params.dfpCode;
                var path = '/' + dfpId + '/' + dfpCode;
                var tag = googletag
                    .defineSlot(path, params.sizes, params.code)
                    .addService(googletag.pubads())
                    .setTargeting('ad_group', biddingHelpers.getAdomikRandomAdGroup())
                    .setTargeting('is_refresh', '0');

                tag.setTargeting('allow_adx', window.UGAPP.bidding.disableAdx ? 'false' : 'true');
                tag.setTargeting('page_type', window.UGAPP.bidding.analytics.pageType);

                if (params.additionalSekindoBehavior) {
                    tag.setTargeting('video', 'sekindo');
                }




                return tag;
            },
            getUnitByCode: function (code) {
                return window.UGAPP.bidding.units.filter(function (unit) {
                    return unit.code === code
                })[0]
            },
            getSlotByCode: function (code) {
                var slots = window.UGAPP.bidding.slots.filter(function (slot) {
                    return slot.code === code
                })

                return slots ? slots[0] : null
            }
        };

        window.googletag.cmd.push(function() {
            window.googletag.pubads().addEventListener('slotRenderEnded', function(e) {
                var slot = biddingHelpers.getSlotByCode(e.slot.getSlotElementId())
                if (!slot) {
                    return
                }

                if (
                    (
                        slot.code === 'ad_cs_2010319_300_250' // tab_desktop tab_pro_desktop для Secindo
                        && [138209404243, 138238546272, 138238996438, 138245687657, 138245691213, 138245902399, 138245692437, 138248215773, 138248239163].indexOf(e.sourceAgnosticCreativeId) !== -1
                    )
                    || (
                        slot.code === 'ad_cs_2010320_160_600' // tab_desktop
                        && [4954799754].indexOf(e.sourceAgnosticLineItemId) !== -1
                    )
                    || (
                        slot.code === 'ad_cs_5723252_300_250' // tab_mobile
                        && [4954799490].indexOf(e.sourceAgnosticLineItemId) !== -1
                    )
                ) {
                    slot.refresh = typeof slot.refresh === 'object' ? slot.refresh : {}
                    slot.refresh.enabled = false
                }
            })
        });
